dc_title_s: 1:24,000 Quadrangle Polygon Boundaries: Russian River Watershed, California, 1996
dc_description_s: This layer represents the polygon coverage of USGS 1:24,000 scale quadrangles that are within the watershed boundaries of the Russian River basin. This shapefile contains the boundaries of the 24k quadrangles of California to be used for geographic reference. Circuit Rider Productions and National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration (2002). 1:24,000 Quadrangle Polygon Boundaries: Russian River Watershed, California, 1996. Circuit Rider Productions. Available at: http://purl.stanford.edu/hf718dn0153 This layer is presented in the WGS84 coordinate system for web display purposes. Downloadable data are provided in native coordinate system or projection.
